## Moderate Issues

### M1. Duplicated Seed/Helper Methods Across Test Classes

The following helper methods are **copy-pasted** across 3+ files with nearly identical implementations:

| Method | Appears in |
|--------|-----------|
| `SeedUserAsync(usernamePrefix)` | `ClaimsEditIntegrationTests`, `ClaimsIndexIntegrationTests`, `UsersEditIntegrationTests` |
| `AddUserClaimAsync(userId, type, value)` | `ClaimsEditIntegrationTests`, `ClaimsIndexIntegrationTests`, `UsersEditIntegrationTests` |

These should be extracted to `TestDataHelper` (which already exists but only covers basic user CRUD). This would reduce ~120 lines of duplication.

