[AntiforgeryTokenHelper.cs:39](file:///Users/colmkenna/Source/IdentityServerStarter/Tests/Integration/IdentityServerAspNetIdentity.IntegrationTests/Infrastructure/AntiforgeryTokenHelper.cs#L39) — The method is `async` but the only async operation is the `await Task.CompletedTask` at the end, which is a no-op. Either make the method synchronous and return a `Task.FromResult`, or remove the `await Task.CompletedTask`.

