### S3. `TestDatabaseHelper` is Unused

[TestDatabaseHelper.cs](file:///Users/colmkenna/Source/IdentityServerStarter/Tests/Integration/IdentityServerAspNetIdentity.IntegrationTests/Infrastructure/TestDatabaseHelper.cs) provides `SeedAdminUser`, `SeedTestUsers`, and `SeedTestClients` — but no test file appears to call any of these methods. Each test class defines its own seed helpers instead. This file is likely dead code.

