## Strengths Worth Noting

- ✅ **Genuine integration testing** — tests exercise the full HTTP pipeline including middleware (CSP headers, route aliases)
- ✅ **Good edge-case coverage** — 404s, empty states, duplicates, validation messages all tested
- ✅ **POST + persistence verification** — tests verify database state after form submissions, not just HTTP status
- ✅ **Clean infrastructure** — `AngleSharpExtensions` and `AngleSharpHelpers` make tests readable and concise
- ✅ **Per-test isolation** — unique DB names via `Guid.NewGuid()` prevent cross-test contamination (in the `IDisposable` classes)
